          "value": "xywh=pixel:451.2631578947368,4029.37496435481,2952.631578947369,1870"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "EXALTED and hallowed be God's great name,\nin the world which God created, according to plan.\nMay God's majesty be revealed in the days of our lifetime\nand the life of all Israel\nspeedily, imminently.\nTo which we say: Amen.\nBlessed be God's great name to all eternity.\nBlessed, praised, honored, exalted,\nextolled, glorified, adored, and lauded\nbe the name of the Holy Blessed One,\nbeyond all earthly words and songs of blessing, praise, and comfort.\nTo which we say: Amen.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
