          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "The WTP Kaddish is marked by long strings of synonyms of praise. The rhythmic repetition of\nthese words is meant to aid one in achieving a higher meditational state. Judith Z. Abrams",
